description:
The Midnight Kitty, Nurse, and Chinese Dress Skin Bundle includes:
- Midnight Kitty costume
- Chinese Dress costume
- Nurse costume

There are no unlock conditions for these costumes. They will become available in-game upon purchase.

*The Midnight Kitty costume, Chinese Dress costume, and Nurse costume are all purely cosmetic.
name: Midnight Kitty, Chinese Dress, & Nurse Skin Bundle
